{"word":"πταῖσμα","slug":"πταῖσμα","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>πταῖσμα</b></el> <el>(πταῖσμα, ατος, τό,) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>a stumble, trip, false step</i>, <b><a href='S:Theognis'>Theogn.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>a failure, misfortune, defeat</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>from <a href='S:πτάξ'><el>πτάξ</el></a>\n"}]}